2014-03-27  wleng  <wleng@pc111>

	* test/mark_partition.c 1.1: rename test-parter.c mark_partition.c

	* include/grid.h 1.1, include/phg.h 1.152, src/Makefile 1.92, src/grid.c 1.1, src/utils.c 1.370, src/vtk.c 1.45, test/test-subgrid.c 1.1:
	Add function of
	1. parallelly import grid,
	2. extract part of parallel grid to be a new grid.

	Test extract subgrid in test-subgrid.c.

	Fixme: inconsistence about phgRank in vtk.c and utils.c.

	* include/partition-utils.h 1.34, src/distribute.c 1.191, src/partition-utils.c 1.121:
	Add a partitioner user.

	The user partitioner does nothing but use the partition information stored in e->mark, which is set by user before redistribute.

	Invoke in cmd: -partitioner user

	A test program test-parter is added to demontrate the usage of part user. It is based on simplest.c, but use the user partitioner to part the grid into 8 parts.

