2008-12-22  liuhui  <liuhui@pc111>

	* src/partition-utils.c 1.44:
	modify module that generates new partitions:
	partitioning points: lo + (hi - lo) /n * i, i = 1...n-1,
	(n = n+1, if [lo, hi] == [x, 1.])
	such that these points are all internal points of [lo, hi].

	* src/partition-sfc.c 1.48: preserve domain ratio
	#if 0 ==> #if 1

