	fix bugs with empty submeshes (call phgMatSetMode in build_G_Pi).

	* include/matvec.h 1.79, src/matvec.c 1.205:
	add function phgMatSetMode() which must be called for using phgMatSetEntry.

	Note: user must call phgMatSetMode(mat, PHG_REPLACE) for using phgMatSetEntry
	      (otherwise if some processes never call phgMatSetEntry then
	      mat->mode is inconsistent which would confuse phgMatAssemble)

	* src/solver-ams.c 1.62, src/solver-phg.c 1.56: update

