2007-02-01  ZHANG Linbo  <zlb@pc111>

	* src/mark.c 1.2, src/utils.c 1.134:
	register options for marking strategies

	* include/mark.h 1.1, include/phg.h 1.44, phg_tcl/Makefile.dep 1.15, src/Makefile 1.25, src/Makefile.dep 1.26, src/mark.c 1.1:
	*** empty log message ***

	* include/quad.h 1.35, src/quad.c 1.110:
	add a new function phgQuadFaceDofDotBas() (untested)

	* src/solver.c 1.173:
	disable the workaround for nlocal == 0 if oem_solver is HYPRE
	(it breaks AMS and HYPRE works without any problem when nlocal == 0)

	* .cvsignore 1.21: update

	* src/solver-hypre.c 1.51:
	finish implementing computation of G and Pi. The use of Pi is by default
	disabled (HAVE_HYPRE_AMS_SET_PI == 0) because it requires a non standard
	function HYPRE_AMSSetDiscretePi provided by the patch file 'hypre-ams-pi-patch'

	The current code works with DOF_ND1, DOF_HC0 and DOF_HC1.
	When HAVE_HYPRE_AMS_SET_PI is nonzero the code works with all types of
	edge elements, but the convergence is slow if order >= 2.

	* src/solver-hypre.c 1.50:
	add Pi, delete G_x, G_y, G_z in HYPRE_PRECOND

	* src/solver-hypre.c 1.49: clean up

	* src/solver-hypre.c 1.48:
	fix the new code for building G and clean up some function names

	* doc/chap5.tex 1.7: update

