	* src/quad.c 1.22:
	use '1' as default quadrature order in phgQuadFaceJump

	* src/quad.c 1.21:
	bugfix: permute the quadrature points in phgQuadFaceJump according to global
	vertex indices for data order consistency.

	* doc/chap3.tex 1.21, doc/chapa.tex 1.47, src/dof.c 1.32, examples/poisson.c 1.210, examples/simplest.c 1.48:
	update

