2005-03-11  ZHANG Linbo  <zlb@pc111>

	* configure 1.34.2.1, configure.in 1.34.2.1:
	Start a new experimental branch.

	The structure GRID is changed to store all elements in a dynamically
	growing array (g->elems). The code seems to be slower than the original
	code, except with a pre-allocation of sufficient space to hold all
	elements.

	The code is not yet fully working and will probably be abandoned later
	(mainly distribute.c).

	* TODO 1.7: update

