	* configure 1.16, configure.in 1.16:
	added libraries required by vtktcl.c on IRIX64

	* Makefile.in 1.14, configure 1.15, configure.in 1.15:
	renabled use of vtktcl.c

	* Makefile.in 1.13, configure 1.14, configure.in 1.14:
	configure.in: tclConfig.sh and tkConfig.sh
	phg_tcl.c: changed 'setenv' to 'putenv', removed inclusion of vtktcl.c which
	requires different libraries with different VTK configurations.

	* Makefile.in 1.12, configure 1.13, configure.in 1.13:
	configure.in: find default VTK paths by running 'cmake'

2004-12-02  ZHANG Linbo  <zlb@pc111>

	* configure 1.12, configure.in 1.12:
	configure.in: comments on CMakeLists.txt

	* Makefile.in 1.11: misc changes

	* Makefile.in 1.10: added config-irix64.sh

	* configure 1.11: added phgSlave function

	* configure.in 1.11: 1. more MPI stuffs
	2. changed phgReturn to be expanded to a single instruction (using dummy if),
	thus no need to enclose phgReturn in curly braces.

2004-12-01  ZHANG Linbo  <zlb@pc111>

	* configure 1.10, configure.in 1.10: MPI support

	* Makefile.in 1.9, configure 1.9, configure.in 1.9:
	MPI support (incomplete)

	* configure 1.8, configure.in 1.8: configure stuffs for MPI

2004-11-29  ZHANG Linbo  <zlb@pc111>

	* Makefile.in 1.8, configure 1.7, configure.in 1.7:
	tested Tcl/Tk support on IRIX (with Freeware Tcl/Tk 8.0, 'cc -32' and 'CC -32')

	* Makefile.in 1.7, configure 1.6, configure.in 1.6: ported to SGI IRIX

	* Makefile.in 1.6, configure 1.5, configure.in 1.5:
	build the library libphg.a

	* Makefile.in 1.5: phg_tcl.c: fixed some issues when VTK is disabled

	* Makefile.in 1.4, configure 1.4, configure.in 1.4:
	autoconf stuffs for Tcl/Tk

	* Makefile.in 1.3, configure 1.3, configure.in 1.3: configure stuffs

	* configure 1.2, configure.in 1.2, Makefile.in 1.2:
	configure stuffs (still need to sort out)

2004-11-28  ZHANG Linbo  <zlb@pc111>

	* Makefile.in 1.1, configure 1.1, configure.in 1.1: autoconf stuffs.

